I mean,

00:26:43.120 --> 00:26:44.600
in relationships

00:26:44.600 --> 00:26:45.920
especially marriages,

00:26:45.920 --> 00:26:47.080
no one can

00:26:48.640 --> 00:26:50.000
stay calm

00:26:51.320 --> 00:26:53.280
and peaceful every

00:26:53.280 --> 00:26:54.720
single day.

00:26:55.520 --> 00:26:56.600
I often

00:26:58.840 --> 00:26:59.720
think

00:26:59.960 --> 00:27:01.400
marriage is like

00:27:01.920 --> 00:27:02.720
a savings

00:27:04.200 --> 00:27:05.200
account at

00:27:05.200 --> 00:27:06.560
the bank.

00:27:07.440 --> 00:27:08.720
Those happy

00:27:09.880 --> 00:27:10.640
moments

00:27:10.640 --> 00:27:11.920
are the "money" you deposit.

00:27:11.960 --> 00:27:13.600
When you argue,

00:27:14.000 --> 00:27:15.080
it's like you're withdrawing

00:27:15.080 --> 00:27:16.200
from that account,

